enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require fetching details about managed sub-accounts, which can be used to set up the test environment.
Depositing assets into a managed sub-account can be used to set up the initial state for snapshot testing.
Withdrawing assets from a managed sub-account can be used to test the snapshot method after state changes.
Fetching sub-account details before and after the snapshot can help verify the accuracy of the snapshot.
